      <hedline>
        <hl1>'True West' Is Closing</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>True West, revival of Sam Shepard's 1982 play at Circle in the Square Theater, announces closing (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''True West,'' a revival of Sam Shepard's 1982 play, is to close after the evening performance on Saturday at the Circle in the Square Theater, 50th Street and Broadway. Directed by Matthew Warchus and currently starring Josh Brolin and Elias Koteas, the play will have run for 154 regular performances and 21 previews.</p>
      </block>
